Express.js – for handling API routes
CORS – to allow frontend requests
Dotenv – for managing environment variables
Multer – for handling image uploads
OpenAI API – for text-based classification
Firebase Admin SDK – for Firestore database integration (if using Firebase)
pg (PostgreSQL) – if using PostgreSQL as a database instead


